<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
diam. Conidiophores reduced to conidiogenous cells. Conidiogenous cells erect, aggregated in clusters on hyphae, hyaline to pale brown, smooth, doliiform to ampulliform, or lageniform, 4.0-12.0 
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
3.0-7.0 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
(x̄ = 6.6 
